The '''2008 Speedway Grand Prix of Europe''' was the second race of the [[2008 Speedway Grand Prix]] season. It took place on May 10 in the [[Alfred Smoczyk Stadium]] in [[Leszno]], [[Poland]].<ref>{{cite web | title = SGP Permanent Wild Cards and 2008 Calendar Announced | publisher = SpeedwayWorld.Tv | date = 2007-10-22 | url = http://www.speedwayworld.tv/en/news/a8612 | accessdate = 2008-04-29 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://archive.is/20070801212439/http://www.speedwayworld.tv/en/news/a8612 | archivedate = 2007-08-01 | df =  }}</ref> The main sponsor was the commercial bank [[Bank Zachodni WBK]].

The Grand Prind was won by [[Leigh Adams]] from [[Australia national speedway team|Australia]]. It was the 7th Grand Prix win of his career. In the final, Adams beat [[United States national speedway team|American]] [[Greg Hancock]] and defending World Champion [[Denmark national speedway team|Danish]] [[Nicki Pedersen]].<ref>{{cite web | title = Adams wins at Leszno | publisher = SpeedwayWorld.Tv | date = 2008-05-10 | url = http://www.speedwayworld.tv/en/news/a9046?SID=2b0e63bdfe41df68647ff3ab2af5be83 | accessdate = 2008-05-11 }}{{dead link|date=January 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

== Riders ==

The Speedway Grand Prix Commission nominated Jarosław Hampel as [[Wild card (sports)|wild card]], and Damian Baliński and Krzysztof Buczkowski as track reserves.<ref>{{cite web|title=Grand Prix Leszno |publisher=PZM.pl |date=2007-10-23 |url=http://www.pzm.pl/Zuzel/Aktualnosci/,c,862,GRAND_PRIX_LESZNO_ |accessdate=2008-04-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514151612/http://www.pzm.pl/Zuzel/Aktualnosci/%2Cc%2C862%2CGRAND_PRIX_LESZNO_ |archivedate=14 May 2008 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref> The draw was made on April 29 at the [[Fédération Internationale de Motocyclisme]] Headquarters in [[Mies]], [[Switzerland]].<ref>[http://www.speedwayworld.tv/draw/2008/draw_pol.php SpeedwayWorld.Tv] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120909232154/http://www.speedwayworld.tv/draw/2008/draw_pol.php |date=2012-09-09 }} - 2008-04-29.</ref> Because of an injury, Bjarne Pedersen was replaced by Luboš Tomíček, Jr.<ref>{{cite web|title=Grand Prix Leszno |publisher=PZM.pl |date=2008-05-06 |url=http://www.pzm.pl/Zuzel/Aktualnosci/,c,862,GRAND_PRIX_LESZNO_ |accessdate=2008-05-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514151612/http://www.pzm.pl/Zuzel/Aktualnosci/%2Cc%2C862%2CGRAND_PRIX_LESZNO_ |archivedate=14 May 2008 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref> Adams, Kasprzak, Hampel and Baliński are all riding for [[Unia Leszno]], whose home track is at the [[Alfred Smoczyk Stadium]], in the [[2008 Speedway Ekstraliga|2008 season]] in Poland.

* Draw No 1: {{flagicon|DEN}} (11) [[Bjarne Pedersen]] → {{flagicon|CZE}} (19) [[Luboš Tomíček, Jr.]]

